		height: 200px;
		width: 200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.doughnut-placeholder {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: conic-gradient(#1152d4 0% 35%, #3b82f6 35% 60%, #93c5fd 60% 85%, #e2e8f0 85% 100%);
